These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: pomegranate, plum, eggplant, pepper, blueberry, mango, tomato
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, malaysian, egyptian, turkish, colombian, british
 1. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pepper is not the colombian##6
 3. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 4. the british is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
 5. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
 6. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person eating plum and the pakistani##7
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the british##1
 9. the egyptian is somewhere between the person eating blueberry and the malaysian##7
10. the malaysian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
11. the turkish is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the left of the british##5
13. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
14. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
15. the person eating blueberry is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | eggplant    | pomegranate    | plum | mango | pepper | blueberry    | tomato |
| Nationality   | turkish | indonesian | malaysian  | colombian   | egyptian    | pakistani | british |

