.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, watermelon, nectarine, peach, spinach, lemon
The people have 7 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, reading, puzzles, traveling, writing, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person eating lemon and the person eating cucumber##7
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating nectarine##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
 6. the person eating spinach is somewhere between the person eating nectarine and the person who's hobby is reading##7
 7. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person eating nectarine and the person eating cucumber##7
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
10. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
11. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person eating lemon##6
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person eating nectarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | lemon  | watermelon | spinach | nectarine | cherry     | peach | cucumber  |
| Hobby   | reading | writing | woodworking  | drawing  | traveling | puzzles      | video-games |

